 a gnome necro and he made a gnome mage.  On Solusek, I have a 24 necro who I always dueled successfully with.  So, I thought this would be a good team because of the 2 tanks, necro with his dots/fears/slows/drains and mage w/ variety of pets for certain situations/ decent dd's and summon ability of certaint items (not a big bonus but can save money and time when summoning food, especially @ lower lvls when you have very little) .  Plus, if were not grouped together, we can always solo.  <br>
<br>
My question:  Is this a good group or am I dreaming?  Of course any group played right is deadly, but would this be a good start?   <br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
